						<summary>

						<p>States that the taxes <hi rend="italic">pērusuṅkam, vaḍḍarāvaḷamu, kolehuvīsālu</hi> etc., due from the village of <hi rend="bold">Kodamagūḍa</hi> to <hi rend="bold">Isāna-Peggaḍa,</hi> the <hi rend="italic">mudiseli</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Kulōttuṅga-Gōmkarāja,</hi> were assigned for the maintenance of worship in the temples and for the support of <hi rend="italic">sanyāsins</hi> and students.</p>						

